{"tid":2327372,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「樓主pin this」根本係一句因自卑而自大既弱智仔先會講既野","createTime":"2020-12-16T04:27:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T05:46:32.000Z","uid":21255,"like":17,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"c540b65e24f882fdd73bf0a19402cbe371ef8b16","tid":2327372,"uid":21255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T04:27:16.000Z","msg":"首先，你講果句野到底有幾精警值得人pin<br />\n好多時候講啲阿媽係女人既野 然後叫樓主pin this<br />\n你句野真係咁精警 人地就自然pin 啦<br />\n<br />\n根本呢類人係現實係冇人認同<br />\n極缺乏自信 要透過網絡虛擬情境自我滿足<br />\n簡單黎講姐係現實極其自卑既毒撚<br />\n但又天真自大到以為自己真係語出驚人 <br />\n果一副打完一個回覆滿心歡喜既自滿樣<br />\n諗下都忍唔住反白眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外 就係一堆人叫樓主pin this<br />\n呢推人仲弱智 完全冇獨立思考<br />\n只懂得跟隨一個虛假概念搖尾乞憐<br />\n從來唔會諗人地既回覆有咩思考位<br />\n冇諗過認真討論<br />\n留一句叫人pin 等自己顯示得好明白人地講咩<br />\n從而睇落冇咁弱智<br />\n<br />\npin 係用黎置頂重要訊息<br />\n唔係俾你班智障係度搵存在感"},{"pid":"10742c96c5d19f6f81a9c3b8ed43bc4f36b88d6f","tid":2327372,"uid":6783,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T04:27:55.000Z","msg":"Pin this"},{"pid":"67244c6bf4b2584e93711dac34a55524640abfcc","tid":2327372,"uid":47783,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T04:28:02.000Z","msg":"講得好<br />\n連囝 pin this"},{"pid":"8f641118cf2b39dcec7f4f367f3f8ea24b00880b","tid":2327372,"uid":249874,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T04:28:43.000Z","msg":"支持 樓主pin this"},{"pid":"2e3fd5e4c0b9b36e178c23df32a02c5ecac1dc08","tid":2327372,"uid":21255,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T04:30:50.000Z","msg":"樓上三個爭住做弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6effd2d71357771f29a7e093659857799605a774","tid":2327372,"uid":143465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20